’ He had said“जाति-जाति में जाति है, जो केतन के पात, रैदास मनुष ना जुड़ सके जब तक जाति न जात”Which would translate something like this that if you were to peel the stem of the banana tree, there appear leaves underneath which form the psuedostem, one can go peeling the leaves forming the stem till there isn’t any tree left at all ! Similarly man has been divided into castes and the human in him has disappeared.
